		"endUncertainty": 0,
		"duration": 46998000,
		"name": {
			"en": "Permian",
			"fr": "Permien"
		},
		"description": {
			"en": "The last period of the Paleozoic, dominated on land by mammal-like reptiles called synapsids. It ended with the Permian-Triassic extinction, the most severe loss of life Earth has ever experienced.",
			"fr": "Dernière période du Paléozoïque, dominée sur terre par des reptiles proches des mammifères appelés synapsides. Elle s'achève par l'extinction Permien-Trias, la plus grave perte de vie que la Terre ait connue."
		},
		"color": "#BE185D",
		"image": null
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"parentPeriodId": 29,
		"start": -251902000,
		"end": -201400000,
		"startUncertainty": 24000,
		"endUncertainty": 0,
		"duration": 50502000,
		"name": {
			"en": "Triassic",
			"fr": "Trias"
		},
		"description": {
			"en": "The opening period of the Mesozoic, when life slowly recovered after the devastating Permian extinction. Early dinosaurs and mammals both appeared, while the supercontinent Pangea remained largely intact.",
			"fr": "Période d'ouverture du Mésozoïque, durant laquelle la vie reprend lentement après la dévastatrice extinction permienne. Les premiers dinosaures et mammifères apparaissent, tandis que le supercontinent Pangée reste largement intact."
		},
		"color": "#78350F",
		"image": null
	},
	{
