		"duration": 58300000,
		"name": {
			"en": "Jurassic",
			"fr": "Jurassique"
		},
		"description": {
			"en": "A period famous for its enormous dinosaurs, including long-necked sauropods and formidable predators. Flowering plants had not yet evolved, but lush fern forests covered much of the warm, humid landscape.",
			"fr": "Période célèbre pour ses dinosaures gigantesques, dont les sauropodes à long cou et de redoutables prédateurs. Les plantes à fleurs n'existent pas encore, mais de luxuriantes forêts de fougères couvrent un paysage chaud et humide."
		},
		"color": "#F97316",
		"image": null
	},
	{
