		"name": {
			"en": "Early Triassic",
			"fr": "Trias inférieur"
		},
		"description": {
			"en": "The opening epoch of the Triassic, when life slowly recovered from the worst mass extinction in Earth's history. Harsh, hot conditions dominated as opportunistic reptiles and amphibians began to repopulate devastated ecosystems.",
			"fr": "Première époque du Trias, durant laquelle la vie reprend lentement après la pire extinction de masse de l'histoire de la Terre. Des conditions chaudes et rudes dominent tandis que reptiles et amphibiens opportunistes repeuplent les écosystèmes dévastés."
		},
